dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.log.proto.DeviceLSRoutingDetails
dataStructure.description:
This association defines the set of LinkStateRoutingProtocols that are currently being used on this LogicalDevice. The supportsProtocol aggregation is used to determine if a particular Protocol (not just a LinkStateRoutingProtocol) is supported by this LogicalDevice. The particular semantics of this association are defined by the DeviceLSRoutingDetails association class.

This association class is optional
dataStructure.label: DeviceLSRoutingDetails
